534
00:35:59,159 --> 00:36:00,820
[SPEAKER_00] i mi imamo drugu varijantu

535
00:36:00,820 --> 00:36:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] da nikad više evropskog novca.

536
00:36:02,619 --> 00:36:03,800
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ovo je period

537
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:04,820
[SPEAKER_00] koji će trajati vjerojatno

538
00:36:04,820 --> 00:36:06,219
[SPEAKER_00] negdje tu do 2030.

539
00:36:06,219 --> 00:36:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] Da mi imamo na raspolaganju

540
00:36:09,420 --> 00:36:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] obilan novac,

541
