544
00:36:13,219 --> 00:36:15,780
[SPEAKER_00] negdje po mojej procjeni

545
00:36:15,780 --> 00:36:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] preko 600 miliona eura

546
00:36:17,199 --> 00:36:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] evropskog novca potrošiti.

547
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo i o tome detaljnije pričati,

548
00:36:20,099 --> 00:36:21,900
[SPEAKER_00] ali sad kad ste spomenuli

549
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:23,780
[SPEAKER_00] laku gradsku željenicu

550
00:36:23,780 --> 00:36:24,360
[SPEAKER_00] ili metro,

551
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:26,320
[SPEAKER_00] ne treba smetnuti suma

552
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:27,340
[SPEAKER_00] da je Evropa

553
00:36:27,340 --> 00:36:28,500
[SPEAKER_00] na takve sustave

554
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:31,300
[SPEAKER_00] sufinancira sa 85%.

555
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:33,679
[SPEAKER_00] I to je jedna povijesna prilika

556
00:36:33,679 --> 00:36:35,239
[SPEAKER_00] koju Zagreb dosad nije imao

557
00:36:35,239 --> 00:36:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] i neće više nikad imati.

558
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:38,360
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo Solun i Sofija

559
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,840
[SPEAKER_00] su zadnji koji su sagradili

560
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] evropske novce metro.

561
00:36:41,739 --> 00:36:42,860
[SPEAKER_00] Solun je svoje otvorio

562
00:36:42,860 --> 00:36:44,679
[SPEAKER_00] za Novu godinu.

563
00:36:44,679 --> 00:36:45,320
[SPEAKER_00] A Solun,

564
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] i onda neko kaže

565
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo pre mali,

566
00:36:47,460 --> 00:36:49,400
[SPEAKER_00] a Solun nema ni 300.000 stanovnika.

567
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:51,420
[SPEAKER_01] Zagreb je jedan od većih gradova

568
00:36:51,420 --> 00:36:52,119
[SPEAKER_01] bez metrova.

569
00:36:52,119 --> 00:36:52,840
[SPEAKER_01] Znate,

570
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] u države u Evropi

571
00:36:54,960 --> 00:36:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] koje nemaju metro

572
00:36:55,599 --> 00:36:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] su bivše,

573
00:36:56,199 --> 00:36:57,360
[SPEAKER_00] to su eksi

574
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] Jugoslavijske države

575
00:36:58,699 --> 00:36:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] i Albanije.

576
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] I mi ćemo ostati

577
00:37:00,880 --> 00:37:01,579
[SPEAKER_00] u toj čakuri.

578
00:37:01,579 --> 00:37:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to je ono što sam rekao,

579
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zagrebu treba

580
00:37:04,019 --> 00:37:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] gradonačni koji ima viziju,

581
00:37:05,300 --> 00:37:06,800
[SPEAKER_00] ali koji ima snage donijeti

582
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] odluku i izvesti je do kraja.

583
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:08,719
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

584
00:37:08,719 --> 00:37:09,320
[SPEAKER_00] to nije,

585
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:09,860
[SPEAKER_00] međutim,

586
00:37:09,860 --> 00:37:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] kad je u pitanju

587
00:37:11,199 --> 00:37:12,440
[SPEAKER_00] izgradnja lake željeznice,

588
00:37:12,440 --> 00:37:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] bit će vidljivi rezultati

589
00:37:14,039 --> 00:37:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] u prvom mandatu.

590
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:15,719
[SPEAKER_00] Jer postoji

591
00:37:15,719 --> 00:37:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] nadzemna trasa,

592
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] devet i nešto kilometara,

593
00:37:18,199 --> 00:37:18,780
[SPEAKER_00] Kvatrić,

594
00:37:18,780 --> 00:37:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] Zračna luka,

595
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] Zagreb,

596
00:37:20,440 --> 00:37:21,820
[SPEAKER_00] koja se može vrlo lako

597
00:37:21,820 --> 00:37:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] realizirati u jednom mandatu.

598
00:37:23,059 --> 00:37:24,300
[SPEAKER_00] Krenatome,

599
00:37:24,300 --> 00:37:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] nije to tako,

600
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] međutim...

601
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:27,860
[SPEAKER_02] A mogu predposljati

602
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:28,739
[SPEAKER_02] da će biti kaos

603
00:37:28,739 --> 00:37:29,400
[SPEAKER_02] na tim mjestima

604
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:30,500
[SPEAKER_02] gdje se to bude gradilo,

605
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:31,480
[SPEAKER_02] da će to biti...

606
00:37:31,480 --> 00:37:33,820
[SPEAKER_02] neće biti...

607
00:37:33,820 --> 00:37:34,820
[SPEAKER_02] Ali treba...

608
00:37:34,820 --> 00:37:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] Neće biti...

609
00:37:35,719 --> 00:37:37,219
[SPEAKER_00] Mi možemo se bojati kaosa.

610
00:37:37,219 --> 00:37:38,179
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećate se one priče

611
00:37:38,179 --> 00:37:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] da će biti kaos

612
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] kad se bude gradio

613
00:37:40,199 --> 00:37:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] Zagrebučki rotor?

614
00:37:41,039 --> 00:37:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećate se te priče?

615
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] Pa godinu dana

616
00:37:44,019 --> 00:37:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] se pumpalo u medijima

617
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:45,719
[SPEAKER_00] da će biti kaos.

618
00:37:45,719 --> 00:37:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se dobro organizira,

619
00:37:46,820 --> 00:37:47,719
[SPEAKER_00] kaosa nije bilo.

620
00:37:47,719 --> 00:37:49,139
[SPEAKER_00] A onda je Tomašević

621
00:37:49,139 --> 00:37:50,280
[SPEAKER_00] četiri godine

622
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:51,340
[SPEAKER_00] objavljao,

623
00:37:51,340 --> 00:37:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] obnavljao

624
00:37:52,059 --> 00:37:53,739
[SPEAKER_00] Jadranski most,

625
00:37:53,739 --> 00:37:54,619
[SPEAKER_00] pa je bio kaos.

626
00:37:54,619 --> 00:37:55,800
[SPEAKER_00] Se ovisi kako

627
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] tko vodi poslovi,

628
00:37:57,159 --> 00:37:57,699
[SPEAKER_00] kako ih organiziraju.

629
00:37:57,699 --> 00:38:00,219
[SPEAKER_02] Ja bih radije imao kaos

630
00:38:00,219 --> 00:38:01,039
[SPEAKER_02] da moje djete

631
00:38:01,039 --> 00:38:01,699
[SPEAKER_02] danas, sutra

632
00:38:01,699 --> 00:38:02,340
[SPEAKER_02] može imati

633
00:38:02,340 --> 00:38:03,699
[SPEAKER_02] normalan gradski prijevoz

634
00:38:03,699 --> 00:38:04,460
[SPEAKER_02] kako spada.

635
00:38:04,460 --> 00:38:05,260
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam spreman

636
00:38:05,260 --> 00:38:06,179
[SPEAKER_02] napraviti taj rizik,

637
00:38:06,179 --> 00:38:08,320
[SPEAKER_02] ali ne znam jeste li

638
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:08,699
[SPEAKER_02] vi kao

639
00:38:08,699 --> 00:38:09,500
[SPEAKER_02] kampišnog načeljica.

640
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:11,039
[SPEAKER_02] Ja se toga ne boli.

641
00:38:11,039 --> 00:38:12,300
[SPEAKER_02] Kako bih rekao,

642
00:38:12,300 --> 00:38:13,079
[SPEAKER_02] dosta je složeno,

643
00:38:13,079 --> 00:38:13,460
[SPEAKER_02] znate,

644
00:38:13,460 --> 00:38:14,000
