[SPEAKER_02] zna da je puno bolje

647
00:38:15,239 --> 00:38:15,380
[SPEAKER_02] neko je.

648
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] Složeno je za onoga

649
00:38:17,380 --> 00:38:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] koji, recimo,

650
00:38:17,980 --> 00:38:18,719
[SPEAKER_00] za Tomaševića

651
00:38:18,719 --> 00:38:19,360
[SPEAKER_00] je sve složeno.

652
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:21,219
[SPEAKER_00] Pa vidite,

653
00:38:21,219 --> 00:38:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] pogledajte bolnicu

654
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] Srebrenjak,

655
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:24,559
[SPEAKER_00] 63 miliona eura

656
00:38:24,559 --> 00:38:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] evropskog novca.

